safedelete: The name of the Special Page for this extension
safedelete-title: Page title to be displayed on special page; $1 is the name of the page to be deleted
safedelete-missingpagename: Displayed when the special page is invoked without the name of the page to be deleted passed as a subpage
safedelete-missingnamespaces: Displayed when global $SpecialDeleteNamespaces is not set
safedelete-cannotdelete: Displayed before the list of links/redirects preventing deletion; $1 is the name of the page to be deleted
